{"tid":2058383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】【日本發起七國集團發聲明】","createTime":"2020-06-10T06:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T09:25:07.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f45a689b1003c5619748ce21df0a4d02a8d5393c","tid":2058383,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"日本首相安倍晉三周三（6月10日）表示，日本希望在七國集團中發起一份有關香港局勢的聲明。中國在香港強推「港版國安法」引起關注。<br />\n安倍告訴國會說：「顯然，我們承認七國集團（G7）的任務是領導全球輿論，日本希望帶頭在香港發表基於『一國兩制』的聲明。」<br />\n日本已經發表聲明，對中國於5月28日中國人大通過的「港版國安法」議決表示嚴重關切，並透過日本駐中國大使表達其觀點。<br />\n由於美中關係因香港問題而趨緊張，東京正處於敏感狀態，因為日本政府計劃邀請中國國家主席習近平進行國事訪問，原定於四月進行訪問，但因冠狀病毒而推遲了訪問。(路透社)<br />\n#港版國安法<br />\n#七國集團<br />\n#安倍晉三<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3911577678916721/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F454004001340790%2Fposts%2F3911577678916721%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVaxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=1889fdfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3911577678916721/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"dbfca0e4919a2ebf42416a8ed579636cdddfb100","tid":2058383,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdf838252c40c6401602c7aeaea9d262bcc8ee3","tid":2058383,"uid":132810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"日本政府支持定反?"},{"pid":"2ac9a9ba297b94236f9d21a52404bf3c8fa87f8e","tid":2058383,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcdf838252c40c6401602c7aeaea9d262bcc8ee3","tid":2058383,"uid":132810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"日本政府支持定反?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"等到月尾G7 咪知"},{"pid":"a16754bf147d2b3e5d4b98ecf6c8dbb6cf7ed352","tid":2058383,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"日本如果收香港難民<br />\n香港應該得返一半人左右"},{"pid":"c4937ef572a988c265d6004a3756509dd8884955","tid":2058383,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86db87c853ec8136bd360b7e8453a053bd159126","tid":2058383,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"如果最後搞到中国唔俾中国人去日本<br />\n日本人定中国人，邊一邊會最唔開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3122e76070a2bab68348e2e782210e77aee7cb","tid":2058383,"uid":37539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16754bf147d2b3e5d4b98ecf6c8dbb6cf7ed352","tid":2058383,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"日本如果收香港難民<br />\n香港應該得返一半人左右"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"如果安置所有香港難民係福島縣，又可能有多難民返香港。"},{"pid":"54528f5b9813fc86960e879e5b59f43d7d541cf6","tid":2058383,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"日本咩料 突然上身?"},{"pid":"745b7741fc8ca454e187496fbb3e28e5da336249","tid":2058383,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"日本<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望</span></span>在七國集團中發起一份有關香港局勢的聲明"},{"pid":"f6edef93bebd16d99fd38a9cf0961a2c43c365d7","tid":2058383,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ac9a9ba297b94236f9d21a52404bf3c8fa87f8e","tid":2058383,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcdf838252c40c6401602c7aeaea9d262bcc8ee3","tid":2058383,"uid":132810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"日本政府支持定反?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"等到月尾G7 咪知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"推遲到九月"},{"pid":"9c743069c075dc6